  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of Clinical Effect of Platelet Rich Plasma Combined With Laser on Acne Scar
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Platelet Rich Plasma may relieve the adverse effect of laser treatment. and it can be
      expected to improve acne treatment result.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
